answers.body_markdown:
The reason that the reason phrase are not being forwarded is due to nginx listening to http2. Http2 does away the reason phrase from http1.1, and the way to solve it will be forcing nginx to listen to http1.1. 

___nginx.conf___
```
...

server {
  listen      [::]:443 ssl;
  listen      443 ssl;

  server_name api.app.com; 
  access_log  /var/log/nginx/app-access.log;
  error_log   /var/log/nginx/app-error.log;

...
```

This will solve the problem of reason phrase not being forwarded.

